{
  "stem": "23815.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So after that, when we finish work, the rest of the people, we went back, again, march to the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I went there, they have a little room there with medicine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know what they had there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I pour something on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was boil like a kettle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Boil.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know what I put there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was painful, maybe because they pour something that it was so bad, the-- the-- the gunshot there, that I didn't want, maybe, I don't know, to have infections or something like that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was-- it was something-- it was boiling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't-- you can't imagine this-- the feeling, you know, the pain I had for-- for being shot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that medicine they put in was a medicine-- look, they could take me-- they could put me in crematorium in the nighttime, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For them, it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One less, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they took me back to the camp, and they did this-- this put on me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for a while I was not doing much, because I couldn't do it with-- with my arm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was not straight away when the beginning was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was already when I was there about a few months, you know, in-- in this Birkenau, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then after that everybody-- I got a little bit better, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I start to work again the same thing, what-- what I was doing before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How did you survive the weekly inspections?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was, I suppose, a healthy person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I didn't have the sickness that they expect me to have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
